usiness-to-business applications. These applications are bringing greater productivity and efficiency to a wide range of enterprise activities.<\/p>\n<p>Several industries stand to benefit from chatbots such as retail, travel and more. In view of unprecedented competition from rivals and disruptive emerging technologies such as augmented reality and virtual reality which are shaping <strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/retail.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">retail IT solutions<\/a><\/strong>. Across several industries, Chatbots are allowing companies to grow their business to meet the needs of discerning and savvy customer base.<\/p>\n<p>This infographic discusses evolution of chatbot and its growing importance in the enterprise world.<\/p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-5908\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Evolution-of-Bot-Technology-00-01-0998-min.jpg\" alt=\"Evolution of Bot Technology\" width=\"908\" height=\"6966\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Evolution-of-Bot-Technology-00-01-0998-min.jpg 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Evolution-of-Bot-Technology-00-01-0998-min-39x300.jpg 39w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Evolution-of-Bot-Technology-00-01-0998-min-768x5892.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Evolution-of-Bot-Technology-00-01-0998-min-600x4603.jpg 600w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Evolution-of-Bot-Technology-00-01-0998-min-300x2302.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>Copy the code to include this detailed infographic of &#8220;Evolution of Bot Technology&#8221; on your blog or page:<\/p>\n<pre>&lt;img src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/Evolution